20do%20taxes%2C'%20and%20the%20work%20was%20not%20groundbreaking%2C%20rewarding%2C%20or%20challenging.%20I%20was%20unproductive%20and%20uninterested%20in%20the%20job.%20They%20call%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-quiet-quit-work-less-get-paid-former-teacher-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equiet%20quitting%3C%2Fa%3E%20nowadays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20considering%20what%20to%20do%20next.%20Growing%20up%2C%20my%20family%20owned%20a%20Chinese%20restaurant.%20I%20missed%20Korean%20fried%20chicken%20in%20Colorado%2C%20which%20was%20so%20good%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20but%20terrible%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223a16485a-d89e-422e-824d-3ae9212ec051%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20decided%20to%20open%20a%20Korean%20fried%20chicken%20franchise%20myself%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkorean-chain-bonchon-chicken-has-the-best-fried-chicken-review-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efranchise%20with%20Bonchon%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20I%20missed%20it%20from%20living%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%20I%20invested%20my%20life%20savings%20into%20opening%20the%20first%20location%20and%20the%20initial%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftopfranchise.com%2Fproducts%2Fbonchon-korean-fried-chicken-franchise%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efranchise%20fee%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20cashing%20out%20my%20401(k)%20of%20around%20%24100%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20underwent%20three%20weeks%20of%20kitchen%20training%2C%20during%20which%20I%20learned%20how%20to%20fry%20chicken%2C%20cook%20the%20dishes%2C%20and%20prep%20the%20veggies.%20Training%20also%20included%20front-of-house%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20opening%20the%20restaurant%2C%20I%20still%20worked%20at%20Microsoft%20but%20quit%20eight%20months%20in.%20As%20a%20senior%20tax%20manager%2C%20the%20salary%20I%20left%20behind%20was%20just%20under%20%24160%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2255178ff3-e73a-49d1-a483-07fb7d9e65d9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAfter%20opening%20the%20first%20location%20in%20Denver%20in%202018%2C%20the%20business%20took%20off%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20all%20the%20franchise%20rights%20in%20Colorado%20and%20now%20have%20six%20locations.%20I%20also%20own%20a%20boba%20tea%20shop%2C%20and%20my%20next%20venture%20is%20opening%20a%2015%2C000-square-foot%20food%20hall%20with%20seven%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20significant%20difference%20is%20that%20in%20corporate%2C%20you're%20expected%20to%20be%20in%20the%20office%20for%2040-50%20hours%20regardless%20of%20if%20you%20have%20work%20or%20projects%20to%20do.%20When%20you%20own%20a%20business%2C%20you%20work%20when%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20opened%20Bonchon%2C%20I%20cooked%20and%20ran%20day-to-day%20operations%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20I%20worked%20around%2060-80%20hours%20a%20week%2C%20seven%20days%20a%20week.%20It%20was%20a%20grind%20for%20the%20first%20year%20because%20of%20the%20steep%20learning%20curve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20I%20opened%20my%20third%20location%2C%20I%20was%20hands-off%20on%20the%20day-to-day%20operations%20and%20relied%20on%20my%20managers.%20I'm%20much%20happier%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20wife%20and%20two%20kids%20and%20can%20spend%20much%20more%20time%20with%20them%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2283d697a3-387a-445f-844f-1c1c70b1890d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20would%20never%2C%20ever%20go%20back%20to%20corporate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20in%20corporate%20is%20like%20being%20stuck%20in%20the%20matrix%3B%20after%20you%20find%20your%20way%20out%2C%20it's%20like%20night%20and%20day.%20You%20can't%20go%20back%20once%20you%20experience%20the%20freedom%20to%20do%20whatever%20you%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20leave%20corporate%2C%20you%20realize%20you're%20capable%20of%20so%20much%2C%20but%20leaving%20the%20security%2C%20steady%20paycheck%2C%20and%20benefits%20was%20scary.%20I%20have%20an%20increased%20net%20worth%2C%20and%20getting%20capital%20to%20expand%20or%20fund%20others%20is%20much%20easier.%20I%20wish%20I%20left%20much%20earlier%20in%20my%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-big-four-accounting-fry-chicken-never-go-back-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743498301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e2fea369253ccddf9a43ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-big-four-accounting-fry-chicken-never-go-back-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20an%20accounting%20career%20at%20Deloitte%2C%20EY%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20PWC%2C%20Henry%20Lee%20quit%20corporate%20and%20opened%20a%20Bonchon%20fried%20chicken%20franchise%20in%20Colorado.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kaila%20Yu)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-big-four-accounting-fry-chicken-never-go-back-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Sikander%3A%20Thinking%20About%20The%20'Bhai'%20That%20Once%20Was%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELike%20a%20true-blue%20star%2C%20Salman%20Khan's%20stardom%20is%20inseparable%20from%20his%20star%20body.%20For%20years%2C%20it%20is%20his%20chiseled%2C%20muscular%20frame%20that%20fans%20revere.%20To%20them%2C%20it%20is%20what%20cinema%20means.%20No%20wonder%E2%80%94as%20Yvonne%20Tasker%2C%20the%20film%20scholar%2C%20notes%20in%20her%20seminal%20work%2C%20Spectacular%20Bodies%E2%80%94the%20action%20hero's%20body%20is%20never%20simply%20flesh%20and%20bone.%20It%20is%20layered%2C%20symbolic%2C%20carrying%20contradictions.%20Khan's%20mythology%20follows%20suit.%20From%20his%20earliest%20days%20on%20screen%2C%20he%20has%20championed%20brawn%20over%20the%20brain%2C%20turning%20gyms%20across%20the%20country%20into%20sanctuaries.%20In%20his%20world%2C%20muscle%20overshadows%20monologue.%20Acting%20chops%20yield%20to%20brute%20strength.%20His%20physique%2C%20more%20than%20his%20expressions%2C%20became%20his%20signature.%20And%20his%20blue%20bracelet%20came%20to%20define%20his%20style.%20Like%20a%20true-blue%20star%2C%20he%20serves%20the%20body%20as%20much%20as%20it%20serves%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Once%20Was%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20wonder%20then%2C%20%3Cem%3EBeing%20Bhaijaan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%202014%20documentary%20exploring%20the%20lives%20of%20three%20die-hard%20fans%20of%20Khan%2C%20opens%20with%20a%20montage%20of%20the%20star%20across%20decades.%20His%20body%2C%20sculpted%20and%20gleaming%2C%20commanding%20the%20screen.%20But%20soon%2C%20the%20tone%20evolves.%20The%20camera%20finds%20Shan%2C%20a%20young%20fan%20from%20the%20small%20town%20of%20Chhindwara%2C%20drenched%20in%20sweat%20at%20the%20gym.%20Through%20the%20unflinching%20gaze%20of%20the%20lens%2C%20his%20form%20is%20studied%20like%20an%20X-ray.%20He%20speaks%20of%20his%20devotion%2C%20his%20dream%20of%20making%20a%20body%20like%20his%20idol's.%20It's%20a%20terrific%20introduction%2C%20layered%20in%20its%20intent.%20On%20the%20surface%2C%20it%20fortifies%20the%20myth%20of%20Khan.%20But%20subtextually%2C%20it%20elevates%20Shan.%20For%20once%2C%20the%20devotee%20stands%20on%20the%20same%20pedestal%20as%20the%20deity.%20Throughout%20its%20runtime%2C%20the%20film%20keeps%20returning%20to%20Khan's%20body%E2%80%94but%20through%20the%20fixation%20of%20his%20fans.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20it%20blurs%20the%20distance%20between%20star%20and%20spectator.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20it%20collapses%20the%20gaze%2C%20binding%20the%20icon%20and%20the%20admirer%20as%20equals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Salman%20Was%20Different%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20sense%2C%20the%20film%20also%20probes%20what%20binds%20someone%20like%20Shan%20to%20a%20figure%20like%20Khan.%20While%20the%20other%20two%20Khans%2C%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20Aamir%20Khan%2C%20became%20icons%20for%20a%20mobile%20generation%20in%20post-liberalisation%20India%2C%20Khan's%20stardom%20emerged%20from%20the%20fissures%20of%20that%20very%20landscape.%20Shah%20Rukh%20is%20the%20beloved%20of%20the%20aspirational%20middle%20class%2C%20and%20Aamir%2C%20the%20thinking%20man's%20hero.%20But%20Khan%20has%20rarely%20found%20favour%20in%20the%20polished%20corridors%20of%20urban%20India.%20The%20reasons%20are%20many%3A%20from%20the%20choices%20of%20his%20films%20to%20the%20turbulence%20of%20his%20personal%20life%20and%20the%20weight%20of%20legal%20controversies.%20His%20kingdom%20was%20never%20built%20in%20metropolitan%20multiplexes%3B%20his%20true%20reign%20lies%20in%20provincial%20towns%2C%20suburban%20sprawls%2C%20urban%20slums%2C%20and%20mohallas.%20For%20the%20working-class%20Muslim%2C%20often%20left%20stranded%20on%20the%20margins%20of%20the%20post-liberalisation%20dream%2C%20Khan%20has%20been%20less%20of%20a%20star%20and%20more%20of%20a%20messiah.%20They%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20couldn't%20board%20the%20train%20of%20upward%20mobility%2C%20who%20watched%20from%20the%20sidelines%20as%20the%20promise%20of%20prosperity%20passed%20them%20by.%20In%20his%20cinema%2C%20they%20find%20not%20just%20entertainment%2C%20but%20affirmation.%20In%20his%20cinema%2C%20they%20see%20a%20rugged%20kind%20of%20hope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Shohini%20Ghosh%2C%20a%20film%20studies%20professor%20at%20Jamia%20Millia%20Islamia%2C%20observes%2C%20Khan's%20rise%20to%20stardom%20in%20the%201990s%20was%20deeply%20linked%20to%20the%20era's%20political%20and%20social%20turbulence.%20It%20was%20a%20time%20marked%20by%20the%20heightened%20communalisation%20of%20public%20life%2C%20as%20the%20Hindu%20Right%20consolidated%20its%20power%2C%20breeding%20anxieties%20among%20Indian%20Muslims.%20Cast%20as%20perpetual%20outsiders%2C%20they%20lived%20under%20the%20looming%20threat%20of%20surveillance%2C%20harassment%2C%20and%20even%20imprisonment.%20In%20this%20climate%20of%20fear%20and%20alienation%2C%20Khan%20emerged%20as%20an%20unlikely%20symbol%20of%20solidarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'Bad%20Boy'%20Of%20Bollywood%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20own%20brushes%20with%20the%20law%20and%20the%20media's%20portrayal%20of%20him%20as%20Bollywood's%20%E2%80%9Cbad%20boy%E2%80%9D%20created%20a%20sense%20of%20familiarity.%20The%20spectacle%20of%20a%20star%20of%20his%20stature%E2%80%94publicly%20shamed%2C%20imprisoned%2C%20and%20devoid%20of%20the%20protective%20sheen%20of%20celebrity%E2%80%94mirrored%20the%20vulnerability%20many%20Muslims%20felt.%20If%20even%20Khan%2C%20with%20his%20towering%20fame%2C%20was%20not%20immune%20to%20the%20unforgiving%20gaze%20of%20a%20polarised%20nation%2C%20what%20hope%20remained%20for%20the%20marginalised%3F%20They%20saw%20their%20own%20defiance%20in%20his%20existence.%20It%20was%20this%20fraught%20kinship%2C%20born%20from%20the%20ruptures%20of%20a%20divided%20society%2C%20that%20cemented%20his%20most%20devoted%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20that's%20why%20Khan's%20bond%20with%20his%20fans%20feels%20so%20visceral.%20A%20%E2%80%9CSalman-Eid%20release%E2%80%9D%20isn't%20just%20about%20a%20film%3B%20it's%20a%20moment%20of%20belonging.%20For%20his%20Muslim%20audience%2C%20it's%20a%20reminder%20that%20they%20matter.%20It's%20a%20reminder%20that%20their%20stories%2C%20their%20traditions%2C%20their%20celebrations%2C%20are%20worthy%20of%20spectacle.%20And%20when%20the%20climax%20arrives%2C%20when%20Khan%20bares%20his%20body%20and%20battles%20his%20nemesis%2C%20the%20image%20transcends%20fiction.%20His%20body%20becomes%20a%20reflection%20of%20both%20their%20fears%20and%20their%20defiance.%20In%20his%20triumph%2C%20they%20glimpse%20strength.%20In%20his%20stature%2C%20they%20find%20significance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Masculinity%20That%20Sold%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20compelling%20intersection%20between%20Khan%2C%20his%20star%20body%2C%20and%20his%20fans%20lies%20in%20how%20it%20engages%20with%20notions%20of%20masculinity%20%E2%80%94%20a%20theme%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20%3Cem%3EBeing%20Bhaijaan%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Khan%20has%20long%20promoted%20a%20macho%20ideal%E2%80%94both%20on-screen%20and%20off.%20In%20reel%20and%20real%20life%2C%20he%20has%20projected%20the%20image%20of%20what%20today's%20generation%20might%20call%20an%20%E2%80%9Calpha%E2%80%9D%20or%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctough%E2%80%9D%20guy.%20His%20films%20exude%20a%20certain%20brand%20of%20conservatism%20that%20conforms%20to%20traditional%20notions%20of%20masculinity.%20It%20is%20this%20very%20ethos%20that%20%3Cem%3EBeing%20Bhaijaan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20directed%20by%20Shabani%20Hassanwalia%20and%20Samreen%20Farouqui%2C%20sets%20out%20to%20explore%2C%20examining%20how%20Khan's%20macho%20persona%20shapes%20modern%20masculinity%20in%20the%20small%20towns%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20documentary%2C%20we%20see%20Shan%2C%20alongside%20Balram%20and%20Bhasker%2C%20speaking%20candidly%20about%20their%20deep%20connection%20to%20Khan.%20In%20their%20words%2C%20a%20striking%20revelation%20emerges%E2%80%94the%20way%20Khan%20treats%20women%20on%20screen%20often%20informs%20their%20own%20perspectives%20on%20gender.%20Shan%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20dreams%20of%20marrying%20a%20girl%20he%20describes%20as%20%E2%80%9Cpure%20and%20shy%E2%80%9D%2C%20an%20ideal%20homemaker.%20Balram%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20admires%20Khan's%20refusal%20to%20kiss%20on%20screen%2C%20reading%20it%20as%20a%20marker%20of%20restraint%20and%20moral%20fortitude.%20For%20them%2C%20being%20a%20man%20means%20protecting%2C%20providing%2C%20and%20embodying%20the%20same%20stoic%20stance%20as%20their%20hero.%20So%2C%20in%20this%20unknown%20pact%2C%20Khan's%20masculinity%20is%20not%20just%20admired%E2%80%94it%20is%20internalised%2C%20adhered%20to%20and%20promoted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Bhai'%20Used%20To%20Be%20Enough%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20readings%20suggest%20how%20Khan's%20male%20fandom%20often%20upholds%20the%20heteronormative%20ideals%20of%20the%20day%2C%20there's%20also%20a%20more%20layered%2C%20even%20subversive%20interpretation.%20The%20reverence%20his%20fans%20hold%20for%20him%E2%80%94for%20his%20body%2C%20his%20presence%E2%80%94carries%20an%20intensity%20that%20many%20may%20see%20as%20bordering%20on%20the%20homoerotic.%20It's%20no%20coincidence%20that%2C%20at%20one%20point%20in%20%3Cem%3EBeing%20Bhaijaan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20fan%20earnestly%20declares%20that%20Khan%20shouldn't%20marry%2C%20fearing%20the%20ripple%20effect%20it%20might%20have%20on%20his%20male%20followers%20who%20remain%20unmarried%20in%20solidarity.%20This%20devotion%20isn't%20just%20admiration%3B%20it's%20a%20kind%20of%20Bhai-code%2C%20a%20brotherhood%20that%20binds%20them%20not%20only%20to%20their%20star%20but%20to%20each%20other.%20No%20wonder%2C%20they%20greet%20and%20part%20ways%20with%20a%20resounding%20%E2%80%9CJai%20Salman%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20as%20though%20their%20affection%20for%20him%20has%20eclipsed%20all%20else.%20The%20actress%20in%20the%20item%20number%20hardly%20matters%3B%20it%20is%20Khan's%20body%20that%20commands%20their%20gaze.%20His%20laughter%2C%20his%20dance%2C%20his%20fury%E2%80%94every%20flicker%20of%20him%20is%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20worth%20noting%20that%20while%20Khan's%20fandom%20often%20appears%20unabashed%2C%20it%20isn't%20entirely%20uncritical.%20Their%20devotion%20can%20fracture%2C%20especially%20when%20his%20actions%20disrupt%20the%20image%20they%20hold%20dear.%20A%20potent%20example%20emerged%20in%20early%202014%2C%20when%20Khan's%20collaboration%20with%20then-prime%20ministerial%20candidate%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20his%20electoral%20campaign%20unsettled%20many%20of%20his%20Muslim%20fans.%20%3Cem%3EJai%20Ho%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20his%20subsequent%20release%2C%20suffered%20the%20impact%20of%20that%20temporary%20discontent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20estrangement%20calls%20to%20mind%20the%20work%20of%20film%20scholar%20Richard%20Dyer%2C%20who%20explored%20the%20inherently%20unstable%20nature%20of%20stardom.%20A%20star's%20image%20is%20never%20singular.%20It%20is%20fragmented%2C%20constantly%20defined%20and%20redefined%20by%20their%20on-screen%20presence%2C%20the%20stories%20spun%20by%20gossip%20columns%2C%20and%20the%20glimpses%20of%20their%20private%20lives%20that%20slip%20into%20public%20view.%20Khan's%20stardom%20is%20no%20exception.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Waning%20Star%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20as%20his%20new%20Eid%20release%2C%20%3Cem%3ESikandar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20hit%20the%20theatres%20last%20Sunday%20to%20an%20overwhelmingly%20negative%20response%2C%20conversations%20among%20fans%20have%20started%20once%20again.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20focus%20is%20on%20his%20ailing%20health%20and%20a%20body%20that%20seems%20to%20betray%20the%20vigour%20it%20once%20commanded.%20Recent%20misfires%20at%20the%20box%20office%20had%20hinted%20at%20this%2C%20but%20watching%20%3Cem%3ESikandar%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20only%20deepened%20the%20perception%20that%20something%20has%20dimmed.%20The%20agility%2C%20the%20kinetic%20force%2C%20the%20muscularity%E2%80%94all%20markers%20of%20his%20stardom%E2%80%94appear%20to%20be%20waning.%20The%20swagger%2C%20the%20nonchalant%20attitude%20that%20once%20attracted%20all%20his%20fans%20are%20now%20nowhere%20to%20be%20found.%20And%20perhaps%20that's%20what%20makes%20him%20a%20true-blue%20star%3A%20one%20whose%20mythos%20is%20inseparable%20from%20his%20inevitable%20descent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Anas%20Arif%20is%20a%20film%20writer%20and%20a%20media%20graduate%20from%20AJKMCRC%2C%20Jamia%20Millia%20Islamia)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743498240000%2C%2