source%2Fabout-tva%2Fboard-of-directors%2Fnovember--7-2024%2F2024-11072024-board-meeting-minutes-signed.pdf%3Fsfvrsn%3Dfde0917c_1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapproval%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20150%20megawatts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20permitting%20applications%20for%20on-site%20natural%20gas%20turbines%2C%20the%20company%20said%20getting%20access%20to%20the%20full%20300%20MW%20of%20grid%20power%20will%20depend%20on%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20infrastructure%20upgrades%26quot%3B%20and%20transmission%20improvements%20in%20the%20region.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20xAI%20has%20been%20supplementing%20its%20power%20supply%20with%20gas-powered%20generators%20from%20Caterpillar%20subsidiary%20Solar%20Turbines.%20These%20produce%20a%20combined%20250%20MW.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ExAI%20can't%20serve%20customer%20needs%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20additional%20on-site%20power%20generation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20permitting%20application.%20TVA%2C%20which%20serves%20electricity%20to%20most%20of%20Tennessee%20and%20portions%20of%20six%20surrounding%20states%2C%20said%20in%20February%20that%20it%20intends%20to%20spend%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tva.com%2Fnews-media%2Freleases%2Ftva-is-building-an-american-made-energy-future%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2416%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20next%20several%20years%20to%20meet%20the%20historic%20load%20growth%20in%20its%20territory%2C%20driven%20by%20power%20demand%20from%20xAI%20and%20other%20data%20centers%20and%20battery%20manufacturers%20expanding%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20its%20on-site%20capacity%2C%20xAI%20could%20likely%20power%20200%2C000%20Nvidia%20H100%20GPUs%2C%20though%20adding%20additional%20computing%20would%20be%20challenging%2C%20said%20Shaolei%20Ren%2C%20an%20electrical%20and%20computer%20engineering%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%20Riverside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20still%20possible%2C%20but%20that%20means%20an%20aggressive%20oversubscription%20strategy%20is%20used%2C%26quot%3B%20Ren%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20practice%20used%20by%20data%20centers%20to%20%26quot%3Boverbook%26quot%3B%20customers%20with%20the%20expectation%20that%20they%20won't%20all%20need%20to%20use%20the%20amount%20of%20power%20they've%20contracted%20for%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20Ren's%20calculations%2C%20one%20million%20GPUs%20could%20require%20over%201%20gigawatt%20of%20electricity%20to%20power%2C%20or%20quadruple%20the%20amount%20xAI%20currently%20has%20access%20to%20in%20Memphis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20an%20LLC%20tied%20to%20xAI%20paid%20%2480%20million%20for%20186%20acres%20of%20land%20south%20of%20its%20initial%20site.%20One%20of%20the%20parcels%20includes%20a%20one-million-square-foot%20industrial%20warehouse.%20xAI%20has%20asked%20TVA%20to%20assess%20the%20site%20for%20access%20to%20260%20MW%20of%20grid%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20MLGW%20CEO%20Doug%20McGowen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.memphistn.gov%2Fwatch-city-council-meetings%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20a%20Memphis%20city%20council%20meeting%20that%20the%20city's%20power%20grid%20might%20not%20be%20capable%20of%20powering%20a%20project%20of%20that%20magnitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20can%20announce%20many%20things%2C%20and%20I%20think%20that's%20important%20for%20our%20community%20%E2%80%94%20that%20we%20get%20excited%20about%20opportunities%20that%20are%20coming.%20But%20as%20you%20know%2C%20there's%20pragmatic%20realities%20about%20a%20lot%20of%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20McGowen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20for%20xAI%20or%20one%20of%20Musk's%20companies%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20Grace%20via%20a%20nonwork%20email%20and%20device%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Agkay%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Egkay%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20through%20the%20enc