%20for%20a%20frightening%2015%20hours%20before%20the%20rescuers%20pulled%20them%20to%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20other%20women%20experienced%20a%20similar%20horror%20when%20they%20waited%20for%20five%20agonising%20hours%20for%20rescues%20to%20find%20them%20under%20the%20rubble%20of%20their%20collapsed%20hotel%20in%20Mandalay%2C%20where%20they%20sat%20crouched%20under%20broken%20ceilings%20amid%20piles%20of%20wreckage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%2C%20who%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20identified%2C%20shared%20their%20borrowing%20ordeal%20during%20an%20interview%20with%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20trapped%20in%20total%20darkness%2C%20but%20the%20good%20thing%20is%20we%20had%20a%20phone%20and%20we%20could%20use%20its%20light%20to%20see.%20If%20we%20didn't%20have%20that%2C%20we%20could%20have%20died.%20We%20could%20see%20to%20clear%20rubble%20from%20on%20top%20of%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20women%20told%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20being%20trapped%2C%20we%20learned%20that%20nothing%20is%20permanent%2C%20and%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20to%20do%20before%20death%20is%20to%20live%20a%20happy%20life%20and%20to%20do%20many%20good%20deeds.%20Don't%20do%20bad%20things%2C%20because%20karma%20will%20follow%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20alongside%20the%20miraculous%20rescues%2C%20tales%20of%20devastating%20losses%20have%20also%20reverberated%20through%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20hundred%20Buddhist%20monks%20were%20crushed%20by%20a%20collapsing%20monastery%2C%20fifty%20children%20killed%20when%20a%20preschool%20classroom%20crumbled%2C%20and%20seven%20hundred%20Muslims%20were%20struck%20while%20praying%20at%20mosques%20for%20Ramadan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESurvivors%20Without%20Food%2C%20Shelter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAid%20groups%20arriving%20in%20the%20worst-hit%20areas%20of%20Myanmar%20said%20there%20was%20an%20urgent%20need%20for%20shelter%2C%20food%20and%20water%20for%20survivors.%20Civil%20war%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20where%20the%20junta%20seized%20power%20in%20a%20coup%20in%202021%2C%20has%20complicated%20efforts%20to%20reach%20those%20injured%20and%20made%20homeless%20by%20the%20Southeast%20Asian%20nation's%20biggest%20quake%20in%20a%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20junta's%20tight%20control%20over%20communication%20networks%20and%20the%20damage%20to%20roads%2C%20bridges%20and%20other%20infrastructure%20caused%20by%20the%20quakes%20have%20intensified%20the%20challenges%20for%20aid%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20hardest-hit%20areas%20...communities%20struggle%20to%20meet%20their%20basic%20needs%2C%20such%20as%20access%20to%20clean%20water%20and%20sanitation%2C%20while%20emergency%20teams%20work%20tirelessly%20to%20locate%20survivors%20and%20provide%20life-saving%20aid%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20UN%20body%20said%20in%20a%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Rescue%20Committee%20said%20shelter%2C%20food%2C%20water%20and%20medical%20help%20were%20all%20needed%20in%20places%20such%20as%20Mandalay%2C%20near%20the%20epicentre%20of%20the%20quake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20lived%20through%20the%20terror%20of%20the%20earthquake%2C%20people%20now%20fear%20aftershocks%20and%20are%20sleeping%20outside%20on%20roads%20or%20in%20open%20fields%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20IRC%20worker%20in%20Mandalay%20said%20in%20a%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20an%20urgent%20need%20for%20tents%2C%20as%20even%20those%20whose%20homes%20remain%20intact%20are%20too%20afraid%20to%20sleep%20indoors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%207.7%20magnitude%20quake%2C%20which%20hit%20around%20lunchtime%20on%20Friday%2C%20was%20the%20strongest%20to%20hit%20the%20Southeast%20Asian%20country%20in%20more%20than%20a%20century%2C%20toppling%20ancient%20pagodas%20and%20modern%20buildings%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20media%20has%20reported%20Myanmar's%20casulties%20at%202%2C065%2C%20wit