and%20child%20sex%20abuse%20material%20--%20came%20into%20force%20on%20March%2017%20as%20part%20of%20the%20government's%20Online%20Safety%20Act%2C%20but%20were%20dismissed%20as%20%26quot%3Btimid%26quot%3B%20by%20critics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIan%20Russell%2C%20whose%20daughter%20Molly%20died%20aged%2014%20in%20November%202017%20after%20viewing%20harmful%20material%20on%20social%20media%2C%20said%20the%20approach%20had%20been%20dominated%20by%20media%20regulator%20Ofcom's%20%26quot%3Bfear%20of%20legal%20challenge%20and%20their%20eagerness%20to%20placate%20the%20tech%20companies%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWorried%20parents%20across%20the%20country%20are%20dismayed%20by%20yet%20more%20half%20measures%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdolescence%26quot%3B%20writer%20Jack%20Thorne%20said%20he%20hoped%20a%20solution%20could%20be%20found%20to%20the%20issues%20raised%20by%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20other%20people%20...%20being%20given%20the%20opportunity%20to%20have%20conversations%20they%20haven't%20had%20before%20and%20that%20they%20should%20have%20had%20that%20might%20lead%20to%20policy%20change%20and%20things%20being%20made%20better%20for%20our%20young%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Sky%20News%20after%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743493260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Foack3m3_adolescence-_625x300_20_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhard-hitting-netflix-drama-adolescence-to-be-shown-in-uk-schools-8059816%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Netflix%20drama%20%26quot%3BAdolescence%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20has%20sparked%20widespread%20debate%20about%20the%20toxic%20and%20misogynistic%20influences%20young%20boys%20are%20expo