FEMA%20funds%2C%20which%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20for%20helping%20Americans%20in%20distress%20from%20national%20disasters%2C%20%5Bwere%20used%5D%20to%20pay%20for%20luxury%20hotels%20in%20New%20York%20for%20illegal%20sustainer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3F%3F%3F%3F%20ELON%20MUSK%3A%20%26quot%3BSomeone%20is%20going%20to%20be%20arrested%20tomorrow.%20He%20actually%20stole%20400%2C000%20social%20security%20numbers%20%26amp%3B%20personal%20information%20from%20the%20Social%20Security%20database%20and%20was%20selling%20social%20security%20numbers%20in%20order%20for%20people%20to%20basically%20steal%20money%20from%20Social%20Security.%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F1hjl1Umcup%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F1hjl1Umcup%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20DogeDesigner%20(%40cb_doge)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcb_doge%2Fstatus%2F1906890456853627376%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%201%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20no%20official%20confirmation%20of%20an%20arrest%20or%20any%20statements%20from%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20regarding%20Musk's%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Musk%20told%20podcaster%20Joe%20Rogan%20that%20Social%20Security%20was%20%26quot%3Bthe%20biggest%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2025%2F03%2F03%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Felon-musk-joe-rogan-podcast.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPonzi%20scheme%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20all%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-claims-360-year-old-man-is-getting-social-security-gets-fact-checked-7852232%5C%22%3Espeech%20before%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March%2C%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20spoke%20of%20%26quot%3Bsh