ur%20lakh%20people%20from%20the%20Social%20Security%20database%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsomeone-is-going-to-be-arrested-tomorrrow-elon-musk-after-4-lakh-social-security-numbers-stolen-8058839%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cars%20carried%20away%20as%20flash%20flooding%20hits%20Greek%20island%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743488906000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fdee7%2Flive%2Fe31ac120-0ebb-11f0-ac9f-c37d6fd89579.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fcx275xnen7no%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Heavy%20rain%20on%20the%20Greek%20island%20of%20Paros%20saw%20cars%20and%20debris%20swept%20through%20the%20streets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fcx275xnen7no%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20India%20And%20Trump%3A%20The%20Two%20Election%20Villains%20That%20Have%20Shook%20Up%20Canada%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20never%20been%20a%20moment%20in%20Canadian%20politics%20when%20a%20domestic%20election%20hinged%20so%20heavily%20on%20a%20single%20external%20factor.%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20dibble-dabble%20on%20issues%20of%20trade%2C%20tariff%20and%20sovereignty%20has%20converged%20in%20Ottawa%20to%20fuel%20a%20national%20backlash%20against%20Washington.%20Trump's%20threats%20against%20Canada%20have%20resulted%20in%20the%20consolidation%20of%20a%20nationalistic%2C%20even%20patriotic%2C%20sentiment%20across%20the%20country%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20boycott%20of%20travel%20to%20America%20and%20its%20products%20at%20home.%20Last%20week%2C%20Canadians%20gathered%20in%20an%20apolitical%20'Elbows%20Up'%20rally%20in%20Toronto%20to%20show%20solidarity%20against%20Trump%2C%20a%20movement%20that%20has%20become%20a%20leitmotif%20for%20resistance%20against%20any%20American%20pressure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20Threats%20May%20Be%20Counterproductive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%20faces%20a%20national%20election%20on%20April%2028.%20But%20interestingly%2C%20in%20less%20than%20a%20month%2C%20the%20poll%20numbers%20have%20changed%20rapidly.%20The%20Liberal%20party%2C%20at%2042%25%2C%20has%20pushed%20slightly%20ahead%20in%20the%20latest%20poll%20numbers%2C%20just%20surpassing%20the%20Conservative%20party%2C%20which%20is%20at%2037%25.%20The%20latter%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20which%20had%20remained%20ahead%20of%20the%20Liberals%20for%20most%20of%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20witnessed%20a%20fortune%20reversal%20owing%20to%20two%20factors%3A%20a%20change%20in%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20Liberal%20party%20with%20Mark%20Carney%2C%20and%20Trump's%20threats%2C%20which%20galvanised%20a%20pan-nation%20sentimental%20consolidation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20threats%20have%20thrown%20the%20domestic%20equation%20between%20political%20parties%20within%20Canada%20in%20disarray.%20It%20has%20not%20only%20given%20the%20Liberal%20party%20some%20unforeseen%20advantages%20but%20has%20also%20complicated%20how%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20parties%20present%20their%20own%20various%20agendas.%20Most%20starkly%2C%20both%20the%20Conservative%20Party%20and%20the%20New%20Democratic%20Party%20(NDP)%20have%20been%20compelled%20to%20appear%20united%20in%20their%20political%20stance%20with%20the%20Liberal%20Party%20in%20dealing%20with%20Trump%20as%20an%20external%20threat.%20Pierre%20Poilievre%2C%20the%20Conservative%20leader%2C%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20Carney.%20Similarly%2C%20Jagmeet%20Singh%2C%20the%20NDP%20leader%2C%20has%20also%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20dissociate%20his%20party%20from%20the%20Trumpian%20threat.%20These%20developments%20have%20catapulted%20Carney%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Liberal%20Party%2C%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20polls%20at%20the%20moment.%20What%20they%20have%20also%20done%20is%20make%20Trump%20and%20the%20US%20the%20most%20important%20subject%20in%20the%20campaign%2C%20eclipsing%20most%20domestic%20issues%20facing%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Call%20With%20Carney%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20lot%20could%20change%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20given%20the%20unpredictability%20in%20Washington.%20Trump%20has%20toned%20down%20his%20rhetoric%20after%20a%20recent%20call%20with%20Mark%20Carney%2C%20in%20which%20the%20latter%20promised%20to%20begin%20comprehensive%20negotiations%20on%20a%20new%20economic%20and%20security%20relationship.%20Trump%20did%20not%20push%20back%20at%20Carney%20with%20either%20claims%20of%20sovereignty%20or%20swipes%20about%20why%20Canada%20should%20become%20the%2051st%20state%20of%20the%20US.%20In%20fact%2C%20Carney%20described%20his%20phone%20call%20with%20Trump%20as%20%E2%80%98cordial'.%20This%20has%20led%20both%20the%20Conservative%20Party%20and%20the%20NDP%20to%20press%20for%20releasing%20more%20details%20of%20the%20grand%20bargain.%20Meanwhile%2C%20a%20high%20pitch%20from%20Washington%20has%20proved%20counterproductive%20for%20Trump%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20Liberal%20Party's%20growing%20political%20consolidation%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20even%20after%20having%20got%20some%20breathing%20space%20from%20Trump%2C%20Canada%20is%20waiting%20with%20bated%20breath%20for%20April%202%2C%20when%20the%20US%20President%20has%20promised%20to%20introduce%20a%20slew%20of%20tariffs%20to%20match%20other%20countries.%20He%20has%20called%20it%20a%20%E2%80%98Liberation%20Day'%20for%20America.%20Already%2C%20the%20US%20has%20imposed%2025%25%20tariffs%20on%20Canadian%20goods%20and%20threatened%2010%25%20duties%20on%20energy%20exports%20from%20Canada.%20An%20estimated%2025%25%20tariff%20on%20cars%20and%20car%20parts%20coming%20into%20the%20US%2C%20which%20will%20go%20in%20force%20on%20April%202%2C%20could%20have%20severe%20repercussions%20for%20the%20Canadian%20economy%3A%20to%20illustrate%2C%20auto%20parts%20worth%20more%20than%20%24300%20million%20cross%20the%20bridge%20connecting%20Ontario%20and%20Detroit%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20The%20Numbers%20Indicate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20factor%20in%20the%20upcoming%20election%20will%20be%20how%20other%20parties%20will%20fare%20in%20the%20mix.%20The%20NDP's%20estimated%20seat%20tally%2C%20as%20per%20a%20poll%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Economist%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20dipped%20from%2018%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20January%20this%20year%20to%20nine%20by%20the%20end%20of%20March.%20The%20Bloc%20Qu%C3%A9b%C3%A9coisis%20(BQ)%20has%20also%20apparently%20slipped%20marginally%20since%20January%20this%20year.%20Simultaneously%2C%20the%20Liberal%20Party's%20rise%20is%20expected%20to%20cut%20into%20the%20other%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Poilievre's%20hint%20that%20his%20party%20may%20align%20with%20BQ's%20Yves-Fran%C3%A7ois%20Blanchet%20before%20the%20polls%20may%20change%20the%20equations.%20Even%20with%20the%20NDP%20declaring%20that%20it%20will%20not%20support%20the%20Conservatives%2C%20the%20primary%20contest%20will%20be%20between%20the%20Liberals%20and%20the%20Conservatives%2C%20with%20the%20former%20playing%20on%20the%20national%20mood%20and%20the%20latter%20banking%20on%20a%20nationwide%20support%20visible%20in%20its%20large%20rallies%20and%20anticipated%20vote-share.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Bogey%20Named%20'India'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20all%20this%2C%20India%20has%20taken%20centre%20stage%20in%20the%20Canadian%20election%20campaign.%20The%20Liberals%20in%20Canada%20have%20not%20missed%20any%20opportunity%20to%20cash%20in%20on%20the%20anti-India%20rhetoric%20that%20sustained%20their%20political%20alliance%20in%20the%20las