against%20concentration%20of%20wealth%2C%20and%20Article%2049%2C%20which%20emphasises%20protection%20of%20places%20of%20national%20importance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMahatma%20Gandhi%20designed%20the%20ashram%20himself...%20embodying%20simplicity%2C%20self-sufficiency%2C%20and%20communal%20living.%20The%20ashram%20exemplifies%20Gandhian%20principles%20of%20sustainability%20and%20harmony%20with%20nature.%20The%20Sabarmati%20Ashram%20stands%20as%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20legacy%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20pivotal%20role%20in%20India's%20freedom%20struggle%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petition%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20had%20not%20been%20accepted%20by%20the%20Gujarat%20High%20Court%20either%2C%20in%20an%20order%2C%20the%20petitioner%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20that%20was%20delivered%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20consideration%20of%20the%20true%20facts%20and%20circumstance%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20then%20had%20noted%20assurances%20from%20the%20state%20government%20that%20existing%20structure%20of%20the%20ashram%20would%20not%20be%20disturbed%2C%20altered%2C%20or%20changed%2C%20and%20noted%20that%2C%20in%20its%20opinion%2C%20the%20redevelopment%20would%20promoted%20the%20ideas%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20present%2C%20the%20dignity%20and%20sanctity%20of%20the%20ashram%2C%20which%20metaphorically%20signifies%20the%20legacy%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20father%20of%20our%20nation%2C%20is%20under%20direct%20threat%20from%20an%20alleged%20redevelopment%20project.%20The%20misuse%20of%20public%20money%20instead%20of%20any%20other%20humanitarian%20purposes%2C%20on%20the%20preface%20of%20development%2C%20is%20against%20Gandhi's%20principles%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petition%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20input%20from%20agencies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%