ith%20Group%20takes%20its%20supply%20chain%20obligations%20extremely%20seriously%20and%20follows%20all%20applicable%20export%20controls.%20We%20maintain%20rigorous%20supplier%20oversight%20and%20supply%20chain%20monitoring%20to%20uphold%20the%20highest%20standards%20of%20compliance%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20company%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alleged%20products%20exported%20to%20India%20were%20for%20use%20in%20a%20satellite-based%20search%20and%20rescue%20network%20that%20supports%20life-saving%20operations%20across%20land%2C%20sea%2C%20and%20air.%20They%20%26quot%3Bare%20not%20designed%20for%20military%20use%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Group%20said%20they%20were%20not%20provided%20any%20evidence%20to%20support%20the%20claim%20that%20its%20products%20were%20shipped%20to%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20apparent%20connection%20is%20a%20common%20Harmonized%20System%20code%20-%20an%20international%20product%20classification%20number%20used%20for%20customs%20purposes%2C%20covering%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20products.%20This%20code%20alone%20does%20not%20show%20what%20the%20product%20is%20or%20where%20it%20originates%20from%20and%20therefore%20cannot%20be%20used%20to%20establish%20a%20link%2C%20which%20the%20New%20York%20Times%20has%20misleadingly%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NYT%20article%20that%20ran%20with%20the%20headline%20%26quot%3BMajor%20Donor%20to%20Reform%20U.K.%20Party%20Sold%20Parts%20Used%20In%20Weapons%20to%20Russian%20Supplier%26quot%3B%20had%20accused%20HR%20Smith%20Group%20of%20selling%20transmitters%2C%20cockpit%20equipment%2C%20and%20other%20sensitive%20technologies%20worth%20nearly%20%242%20million%20to%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20UK%20and%20US%20had%20banned%20such%20sales%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20shipments%20reportedly%20went%20via%20Hindustan%20Aeronautics%20Limited%20-%20and%20had%20the%20%26quot%3Bsame%20identifying%20product%20codes%26quot%3B.%20The%20report%20claimed%20that%20HAL%20received%20118%20shipments%20from%20HR%20Smith%20Group%20between%202023%20and%202024%2C%20and%20sent%2013%20shipments%20of%20the%20same%20products%20to%20Rosoboroneexport%2C%20a%20Russian%20arms%20agency%20blacklisted%20by%20the%20US%20and%20UK%2C%20during%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHAL%20has%20not%20yet%20responded%20to%20the%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20had%20earlier%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20report%20was%20%26quot%3Bfactually%20incorrect%20and%20misleading%26quot%3B.%20Accusing%20the%20US-based%20outlet%20of%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Bdistort%20facts%20to%20suit%20a%20political%20narrative%26quot%3B%2C%20they%20said%20HAL%20had%20followed%20all%20international%20obligations%20on%20strategic%20trade%20controls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20also%20urged%20%26quot%3Breputed%20media%20outlets%20to%20undertake%20basic%20due%20diligence%20while%20publishing%20such%20reports.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743488100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fufb8nq58_hr-smith-group-sensitive-tech-sales-hal-russia-nyt-story_625x300_31_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-firm-trashes-new-york-times-report-on-sensitive-tech-transfer-to-russia-via-hal-8058614%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22British%20aerospace%20manufacturer%20HR%20Smith%20Group%20has%20slammed%20a%20New%20York%20Times%20report%20that%20accused%20it%20of%20transferring%20sensitive%20technology%20to%20a%20blacklisted%20agency%20supplying%20Russia%20with%20weapons%20via%20an%20Indian%20state-run%20company.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-firm-trashes-new-york-times-report-on-sensitive-tech-transfer-to-russia-via-hal-8058614%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Priyadarshan