0at%20the%20age%20of%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20yoghurt%20that%20people%20with%20PCOS%2C%20like%20myself%2C%20or%20any%20other%20health%20problems%2C%20could%20trust%2C%20one%20that%20was%20free%20of%20preservatives%20or%20added%20sugar%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20conducted%20extensive%20research%20online%2C%20consulted%20with%20nutritionists%2C%20and%20visited%20the%20farm%20where%20she%20sources%20her%20milk%20to%20carefully%20choose%20the%20best%20ingredients.%20%E2%80%9CA2%20milk%20was%20the%20best%20choice%20because%20it%20has%20a%20higher%20protein%20content%20and%20is%20better%20for%20the%20gut%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20science%20behind%20A2%20milk%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Samrakshini%20G%2C%20a%20gynaecologist%20and%20fertility%20specialist%20based%20in%20Bengaluru%20with%2010%20years%20of%20experience%2C%20sheds%20light%20on%20the%20ongoing%20debate%20surrounding%20the%20type%20of%20milk%20we%20consume.%20She%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CMilk%20is%20classified%20into%20two%20types%2C%20A1%20and%20A2%2C%20distinguished%20by%20a%20single%20protein%20known%20as%20beta-casein.%20The%20difference%20between%20the%20two%20lies%20in%20a%20variation%20of%20just%20one%20amino%20acid.%E2%80%9D%20In%20A1%20milk%2C%20the%20amino%20acid%20at%20position%2067%20is%20histidine%2C%20while%20in%20A2%20milk%2C%20it%20is%20proline.%20This%20seemingly%20small%20difference%20plays%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20the%20digestion%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC9393-1_11zon-1743132614-500x750.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jogurt%20contains%20monk%20fruit%20instead%20of%20sugar%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fe