ted%20for%2016%20hours%20in%20winter%20and%2010%20hours%20in%20summer%20to%20develop%20the%20perfect%20consistency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC01390-1_11zon-1743132730-500x750.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jogurt%20currently%20includes%2011%20flavours%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC01390-1_11zon-1743132730-500x750.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC01390-1_11zon-1743132730-200x300.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC01390-1_11zon-1743132730-768x1152.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC01390-1_11zon-1743132730-1024x1536.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC01390-1_11zon-1743132730-1365x2048.jpg%201365w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC01390-1_11zon-1743132730-1200x1800.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC01390-1_11zon-1743132730-150x225.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FDSC01390-1_11zon-1743132730.jpg%201660w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-416456%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJogurt%20currently%20offers%2011%20flavours%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20step%20involves%20straining%20the%20yoghurt%20to%20separate%20the%20thickened%20portion%2C%20then%20whisking%20it%20to%20achieve%20a%20smooth%20consistency.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20double-strain%20it%20to%20achieve%20the%20Greek%20yoghurt%20consistency%2C%20leaving%2015%20grams%20of%20protein%20per%20100-gram%20cup