is%20even%20bigger.%20By%202030%2C%20the%20programme%20aims%20to%20establish%201%2C00%2C000%20women-led%20enterprises%20and%201%2C000%20women-driven%20e-rickshaw%20services%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20creating%201%20million%20jobs%20in%20the%20process.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20realise%20this%20vision%2C%20the%20group%20has%20tied%20up%20with%20women%E2%80%99s%20institutions%20like%20SHGs%20(Self%20Help%20Groups)%20and%20CLFs%20(Cluster%20Level%20Federations)%20facilitated%20by%20SRLMs%20and%20partners%20like%20Gates%20Foundation%2C%20Bajaj%20Finserv%2C%20and%20Work4Progress%20launched%20collaboratively%20with%20%E2%80%9Cla%20Caixa%E2%80%9D%20Foundation.%20For%20women%20like%20Anita%2C%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20statistic%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20movement.%20A%20movement%20to%20rewrite%20the%20rules%20of%20what%20women%20and%20youth%20can%20achieve%20in%20rural%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20ensure%20that%20anyone%20with%20any%20kind%20of%20a%20unique%20experience%20is%20able%20to%20build%20a%20library%20of%20livelihoods%20themselves.%20Instead%20of%20asking%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20will%20the%20future%20of%20work%20look%20like%20for%20people%3F%E2%80%9D%20we%E2%80%99re%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20decide%20for%20yourself%20by%20becoming%20entrepreneurial.%20We%20believe%20in%20collective%20action%20where%20we%20scale%20entrepreneurial%20ecosystems%20through%20collaboration%20using%20the%20combined%20strengths%20of%20all%20the%20partners%20that%20work%20with%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20sums%20up%20Kanika%20Verma%2C%20Lead%E2%80%93Green%20and%20Inclusive%20Entrepreneurship%20and%20Associate%20Vice%20President%2C%20Development%20Alternatives%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWatch%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fshorts%2FJk3_1PGhprM%3Ffeature%3Dshare%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20know%20more.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%